    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1943-08-02T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1943-08-02T00:00:00-05:00" n="195"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d195">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">Roosevelt Papers: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">President <persName type="from">Roosevelt</persName> to Prime
                        Minister <persName type="to">Churchill</persName>
                    </hi>
                    <note n="1" xml:id="d195fn1">Sent to the <gloss target="#t_White1">White</gloss>
                        House Map Room, Washington, and forwarded to the United States Naval
                        Attaché, London, via Navy channels.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">secret</hi>
                        <lb/>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">priority</hi>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Birch Island, Ontario</hi>
                        </placeName>,] <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-08-02">August 2,
                            1943</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Number 340 from the President to the <gloss target="#t_FNP1">Former Naval
                        Person</gloss>. Personal and secret.</p>
                <p>I fully approve of the text of your proposed announcement upon arrival of “<gloss
                        target="#t_Quadrant1">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Quadrant</hi>
                    </gloss>” party as given in your 396.<note n="2" xml:id="d195fn2">
                        <hi rend="italic">Ante</hi>, <ref target="#pg_406">p. 406</ref>.</note>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Roosevelt</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
